'''甚小孔径终端'''（'''V'''ery '''S'''mall '''A'''perture '''T'''erminal，VSAT）是指天線口徑為3米以下的小型地球站。常見的VSAT天線口徑為1.2米，由碟型天線、用戶電腦和作介面的室內單元組成。最高下行數據率可達16Mbit/s，與[[ADSL|ADSL]]相若。<ref>{{cite| url= http://www.globaltt.com/en/services_vsat.html| title= What is VSAT - GlobalTT| accessdate= 2015-07-22| archive-date= 2016-10-21| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20161021124601/http://www.globaltt.com/en/services_vsat.html| dead-url= no}}</ref>VSAT終端以[[地球同步衛星|地球同步衛星]]連接其他終端（[[網狀網絡|網狀網絡]]）或一個作為集線器的主地球站（[[星型網|星型網]]），以傳輸寬頻訊號，提供[[互聯網存取|互聯網存取]]、[[VOIP|VOIP]]、影像等服務。<ref>{{cite |url =http://searchmobilecomputing.techtarget.com/definition/VSAT |title =What is VSAT (Very Small Aperture Terminal)? - Definition from WhatIs.com |accessdate =2015-07-22 |archive-date =2021-01-25 |archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20210125145413/https://searchmobilecomputing.techtarget.com/definition/VSAT |dead-url =no }}</ref>

==應用==
VSAT可用以提供[[宽带上网|宽带上网]]的服务。VSAT技术的优点是容易配置，只要在卫星讯号的覆盖区之内，与卫星保持直视线（Line of sight），就可以在2小时之内建立通讯连线。只需要将[[碟型天线|碟型天线]]面向卫星，启动内建数据机，就可以如[[光纤|光纤]]或[[DSL|DSL]]一样的连线。<ref>{{cite news |url = http://www1.voanews.com/chinese/news/science-technology/ustroops-HIGH-SPEED-INTERNET-20091223-80010287.html |title = 科技脉动：驻伊阿美军将能高速上网 |work = VOA |date = 2009-12-23 |accessdate = 2009-12-23 |archive-date = 2010-06-08 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100608123628/http://www1.voanews.com/chinese/news/science-technology/ustroops-HIGH-SPEED-INTERNET-20091223-80010287.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>

